What is your mywc program test plan?

mywc001.txt: words with increasing spaces between them one th first line 
             and decreasing spaces on the second line. Tests the ability 
             of the prorgam to handle consecutive spaces without messing up
             word count

mywc002.txt: normal file with no '\n' on the second line. Tests the program's
             ability to count new line characters

